            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p data-vmark="dc56">【更新】官方放出了新的海报：</p><p data-vmark="4b60" style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2023/12/f806b9f1-8e36-4d04-9d56-b006e41a2de9.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" w="1080" h="1350" title="《辐射》真人剧集新海报：女主角路西踏出避难所" width="1080" height="1025" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p data-vmark="3302" style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2023/12/71df9f2c-b4e9-43f4-9d4b-c4f42122638e.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" w="1080" h="1350" title="《辐射》真人剧集新海报：女主角路西踏出避难所" width="1080" height="1025" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p data-vmark="6287"><a class="s_tag" href="https://www.ithome.com/" target="_blank"></a></p><p data-vmark="e32b" style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2023/12/588a05d6-6dbf-456f-97d1-cc411ddc911c.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" w="1080" h="1350" title="《辐射》真人剧集新海报：女主角路西踏出避难所" width="1080" height="1025" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p data-vmark="c115"><a class="s_tag" href="https://www.ithome.com/" target="_blank">IT 之家</a> 12 月 2 日消息，《辐射》真人剧集将在 2024 年&nbsp;4 月 12 日上线亚马逊 Prime Video。IGN 今日发布了该剧集的宣传海报。</p><p data-vmark="cdd0" style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2023/12/78d842de-73bb-4643-8d98-0e91f028fc02.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" w="972" h="1440" title="《辐射》真人剧集新海报：女主角路西踏出避难所" width="972" height="1215" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p data-vmark="2f4e">如上图所示，海报中的人物是女主角路西，由英国女演员艾拉・珀内尔（Ella Purnell）饰演。据介绍，路西是一位乐观的避难所居民，具有美式进取精神。故事背景是核战&nbsp;200 年后，豪华避难所里的居民被迫返回受辐射的地面，一个极其复杂、怪异且暴力的世界正在等待着他们。</p><p data-vmark="e518">日前，Vanityfair 放出了该剧集的剧照：</p><p data-vmark="81a3" style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2023/11/0a48316a-01e7-4915-b471-9592fe627ffa.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" w="1440" h="596" title="《辐射》真人剧集新海报：女主角路西踏出避难所" width="1440" height="339" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p data-vmark="1e12" style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2023/11/e1eb260d-a542-4de5-a3b8-08b14197895b.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" w="1440" h="959" title="《辐射》真人剧集新海报：女主角路西踏出避难所" width="1440" height="546" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p data-vmark="2d79" style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2023/11/48c4ed96-15fe-4029-8953-1c1277a2ce27.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" w="1440" h="595" title="《辐射》真人剧集新海报：女主角路西踏出避难所" width="1440" height="339" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p data-vmark="d10c" style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2023/11/9af43666-12ad-4016-bd94-9fd8423b607b.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" w="1440" h="595" title="《辐射》真人剧集新海报：女主角路西踏出避难所" width="1440" height="339" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p data-vmark="2f9f" style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2023/11/d7221513-a450-48b3-8fa0-c4d86605aa32.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" w="1440" h="595" title="《辐射》真人剧集新海报：女主角路西踏出避难所" width="1440" height="339" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p data-vmark="8414" style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2023/11/b0e5a8d6-6806-4971-9f6d-8e1824742da9.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" w="1440" h="595" title="《辐射》真人剧集新海报：女主角路西踏出避难所" width="1440" height="339" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p data-vmark="6ba9" style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2023/11/9f30c4d9-d98d-4e3c-b703-3a5ed2e30bb0.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" w="1440" h="595" title="《辐射》真人剧集新海报：女主角路西踏出避难所" width="1440" height="339" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p data-vmark="b49d" style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2023/11/5fab6a54-4a43-4888-aa1d-6f35f85efc08.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" w="1440" h="595" title="《辐射》真人剧集新海报：女主角路西踏出避难所" width="1440" height="339" referrerpolic